<![CDATA[
	<div><t_head1><app /></t_head1> <version />
	<br /><t_splitter><br />
	<br />NFCard can read contactless IC card use NFC hadware.<br />
	<br />Support ISO7816-4, Felica compliant e-purse/e-cash, It can read account validity, offline balance and transaction logs from these cards if no read restriction.<br />
	<br />So far we\'ve confirmed the following can be read: Shenzhen Tong (newer version) of Shenzhen, Shanghai Card, Octopus Card of Hongkong, Beijing Municipal Card (newer version), Changan Card of Shaanxi,Xi\'an, Wuhan City Smart Card, Quickpass (China, e-cash), T-Union (China, e-purse & e-cash), City Union (China).<br />
